 Mopidy is a music server which can play music from Spotify or from your
 local hard drive. To search for music in Spotifyâ€™s vast archive, manage
 playlists, and play music, you can use any MPD client. MPD clients are
 available for most platforms, including Windows, Mac OS X, Linux, and iPhone
 and Android phones.

